          <td width="689" valign="top" background="images/bg01.jpg"> <p> 
              <B><font color='#FF3300' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='2'>Recruitment Now Open<BR></B></font><font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='1'>2003-07-08 15:07:41&nbsp;-&nbsp;<font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='1'><I>Furor 'Jimmy' Planedefiler</I>&nbsp;              </font><br>
              <img src="images/content_bar.jpg" width="645" height="1"></p>
            <p>
<font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='2'>		
Due to the fact that it is no longer possible to raid with 40-50 people and have anything more than limited success, we have opened up recruitment.<br />
<br />
Read the following and follow the instructions. There ARE requirements which you will need to meet to be considered for recruitment. Those requirements will be related to you during your interview phase with one of the recruitment officers.<br />
_________________________________________<br />
In-Server Recruitment is now open. We are looking for the following classes:<br />
<br />
Clerics (6-8)<br />
Warriors (3)<br />
Monks (3)<br />
Rogues (3)<br />
Paladins (3)<br />
Shadowknights (3)<br />
Bards (4)<br />
Enchanters (2)<br />
Wizards (Unlimited)<br />
Magicians (1)<br />
Rangers (2)<br />
Beastlords (3)<br />
Necromancer (3)<br />
Druid (3)<br />
Shaman (2)<br />
<br />
Please note this is RECRUITMENT only - not everyone will make the cut, hence the high number of recruits allowed. <br />
<br />
Flagging will be done from Grummus to the Rathe and our main focus will be on Time B once flagging is complete.<br />
<br />
Xservers will ONLY be taken from reccommendations via current tenured Xserver members. We will not be accepting any other type of Xserver (i.e. if you don't have an Xserver friend in this guild, you have no chance, sorry).<br />
<br />
If you are interested you will need to contact one of the following people in game: Furor, Frozboz, Sirensa, or Sylvos. You may speak with other members if none of those people are online but you will ultimately have to deal with one of those 4 individuals.<br />
<br />
______________________________________________<br />
<br />
We will NOT be accepting every recruit. I simply cannot stress this enough. You will be competing with other recruits for positions in the guild. We want people with brains and the ability to use logic and critical thinking during their play sessions. <br />
<br />
Additionally, if you are a 'Drama Queen,' don't bother. We have enough of those already...<br />
<br />
<br />
-The Management<br />
</font>
			
